{"title":"丁秋秋班赶送战饭","authors":["复正"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":4,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁秋秋班赶送战饭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"·复正·"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁秋秋是泰山部的一个炊事班长，赵家场战斗时，亲往火线送饭，并参加突击组，被选为特等工作模范，他的事迹详见太行文艺杂志三卷二期。现在他正努力创造一个模范班。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——编者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当英雄，真不易，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手得勤，心得细；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不光自己干的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要推动别人把功立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的英雄不多见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把丁秋秋故事提一提："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打下赵家场庆胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰山都又把英雄比，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄模范数谁好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数着秋秋是第一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄会上受奖励，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奖品得有一簸箕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛巾、袜子、铅笔、肥皂样样有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那模范牌儿亮亮的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"模范牌他保存起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志问他为啥哩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一个头开不了满山荒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个巴掌怎能拍响哩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣本是全班的事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作是大伙搞成的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推动全班都立功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐把牌牌带上去。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁秋秋带着奖品回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到班就找老马兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫声：“守福同志快来看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这条毛巾密不密？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老马抿嘴嘻嘻笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连说：“班长你真光荣哩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这毛巾又白又软又细密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好把它保存起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是英雄的好标记！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋秋连忙开言道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“干工作你最积极，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这条毛巾送给你。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老马一听心里急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙说：“那能要你的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是你的光荣奖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用我再去买去。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋秋不听他言语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底拉拉扯扯送了礼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回身又忙叫老李："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这双袜子你穿去！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剩下肥皂和铅笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又给老周老岳送了去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分罢奖品开个会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋秋又忙把话提："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“打老蒋，去杀敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的百姓不受恶霸欺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全班怎样做的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家多想好主意。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志齐声说同意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争着都把意见提。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“保证不做生菜饭”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“保证开水按时给，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有人要学丁班长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭菜送上火线去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你积极我更卖力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个跟着一个比。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日头偏了西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭菜要送到阵地里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋秋正想担上走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周春生拉住他的衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“班长害眼看不清路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我和老李不用你！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说着抢过杠子桶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬上全连的热米饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼扇呼扇跑头里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事务长担上菜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟在后面走的急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路说来一路笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼到了目的地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士闻见香味眯眯笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边夸老周和老李。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭锅刚刚地上放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然奉命挪阵地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刷拉拉全连转移走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送饭的三人直叹气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥时能够吃上饭？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍饥跑路使不的。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越思越想越不忍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬起饭菜撵上去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上坡下坡不好走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不顾那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长喊他们往后去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越跑越快心越急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭锅抬到顶前头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个饭碗盛的急。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日头沉的没了影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四面都是黑漆漆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他三人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼扇呼扇窜的紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼呼喘喘透不过气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过大坡，下凹地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一脚高，一脚低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队伍走着他们又跟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到饭没剩一粒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们吃的饱又饱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他三人累的汗直滴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阎排长，心里感动直夸好；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“行军吃饭真稀奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当兵十年头一次见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们要："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多杀蒋贼把功立！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}